                <head>408. Unofficial Record of Discussion at the <gloss target="#t_AID_1"
                        >AID</gloss> Executive Staff Meeting, April 5<note n="1" type="source"
                        xml:id="d408fn1">“Development Loan Terms.” Official Use Only. 1 p.
                        Washington National Records Center, <gloss target="#t_RG_1">RG</gloss> 286,
                            <gloss target="#t_AID_1">AID</gloss> Administrator Files: <gloss
                            target="#t_FRC_1">FRC</gloss> 65 A 481, Development Financing, <gloss
